query: SELECT documentViews.id, documentViews.documentId, documentViews.trackingId, documentViews.viewedAt, documentViews.ipAddress, documentViews.userAgent, documentViews.duration, documentTracking.id, documentTracking.documentId, documentTracking.trackingToken, documentTracking.viewCount, documentTracking.firstViewedAt, documentTracking.lastViewedAt, documentTracking.viewerIp, documentTracking.viewerUserAgent, documentTracking.createdAt FROM documentViews INNER JOIN documentTracking ON documentViews.trackingId = documentTracking.id ORDER BY documentViews.viewedAt DESC LIMIT 20;
